These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, spinach, broccoli
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Food   | cucumber | spinach | broccoli |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, climbing, surfing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Sport   | water-polo | surfing | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, white, green
1. the person who likes green is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Color   | white | red | green |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
