.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, chess
1. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |   3    |
| Game   | backgammon | bridge | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, november, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Birthday   | may | november | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, roller, tram
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |       2       |  3  |
| Transport   | taxi | roller | tram |

