.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-10::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, zombie
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | satire | zombie |

