.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, juice
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking soy-milk##2
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | juice | soy-milk |

